	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When coming across those boards normally, the "new posts" are marked in orange.
<br />Those new posts can be in any topic in any forum, and are *supposed* to keep marked until you read them.
<br />However, for me, when I click on the first one *ALL* new posts get unmarked, making to me the task harder to know what's new since the last one. It's REAL frustrating.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


